# Assignment 1 - Espresso Store Sales Data Analysis

This project involves analyzing order and customer data from an espresso store to uncover business insights and optimize sales strategies.

## Tasks Performed

1. Format amount and date columns
2. Sort orders by city and amount; filter by conditions
3. Retrieve shipping state for specific customer
4. Classify orders as "Most Demanded" or "Least Demanded"
5. Analyze age group 30-40 orders and extract order ID segments
6. Replace category names
7. Calculate new order dates (3 months later)
8. One-Way Data Table (Loan & Interest)
9. Goal Seek (profit target scenario)
10. Pivot Table & Chart: Sales summary by month and age group

